title: Mórahalom VSE
text: Mórahalom Városi Sportegylet is a professional <a href="Association%20football">football</a> club based in <a href="M%C3%B3rahalom">Mórahalom</a>, <a href="Csongr%C3%A1d%20County">Csongrád County</a>, <a href="Hungary">Hungary</a>, that competes in the <a href="Nemzeti%20Bajnoks%C3%A1g%20III">Nemzeti Bajnokság III</a>, the third tier of <a href="Hungarian%20football%20league%20system">Hungarian football</a>.
